NK036(chi)029:1: // bla ma dam pa ku ma r+aa dza de nyid /
NK036(chi)029:2: dwags po dang lung gi phur sku 'das pa'i tshul bstan pa'i tshe /
NK036(chi)029:3: phyi rabs kyi don du 'das rjes gsungs pa /
NK036(chi)029:5: +aahh+aum sprang po bya bral gzhon nu rgyal pos gdams pa ni //
NK036(chi)029:6: e ma ngas ni ngo bo skyong 'ded rang rig rtsa gdar bcad //
NK036(chi)029:7: dmigs med spros bral mtha' dang bral bar rtogs //
NK036(chi)029:8: chos sku'i ngang du ku ma r+aa dza 'chi //
NK036(chi)029:9: rang bzhin dbyings la lta stangs rig pa gcun //
NK036(chi)029:10: zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor thig le nyag gcig rtogs //
NK036(chi)029:11: longs sku'i ngang du ku ma r+aa dza 'chi //
NK036(chi)029:12: thugs rjes sems can gzhan phan gtso bor byas //
NK036(chi)029:13: shar grol rig pa chos nyid ma dang 'phrad //
NK036(chi)029:14: sprul sku'i ngang du ku ma r+aa dza 'chi //
NK036(chi)029:15: ye thog dang po'i sangs rgyas dri ma med //
NK036(chi)029:16: gzhir snang rang gdangs dang po'i byung sar thim //
NK036(chi)029:17: lhun grub sbubs su ku ma r+aa dza 'chi //
NK036(chi)029:18: nga yi zab don snying po'i gdams pa rnams //
NK036(chi)029:19: bcud du dril nas nyams len snying por bstan //
NK036(chi)029:20: bdag gi rjees 'jug skal ldan snying gi bu //
NK036(chi)029:21: ji ltar bsgrubs kyang chos dang mthun par mdzod //
NK036(chi)029:22: nga yi gtam bzhugs 'gro kha'i tshig 'di rnams //
NK036(chi)029:23: phyi rabs don du snying nas mos la ston //
NK036(chi)029:24: tig tig gang la yang mi 'dug /
NK036(chi)029:25: lar snang ba 'di gtad pa med pa gcig yin //
NK036(chi)029:26: skyag pa ngas drin chen rin po che //
NK036(chi)029:29: ces gsungs nas thugs 'pho ba'i tshul bstan te /
NK036(chi)029:30: sa chen po 'di rab tu g.yos /
NK036(chi)029:31: nam mkha' la sil snyan gyi sgra rang grags /
NK036(chi)029:32: 'ja' tshon gyi gur phub ste 'gro ba rnams ngo mtshar gyi sa la bkod //
NK036(chi)029:34: +aahmh'uhgu ru ku ma r+aa dza la na mo //
NK036(chi)029:35: gdod ma'i mgon dang rnam dbyer mi phyed cing //
NK036(chi)029:36: rig 'dzin chen po bi ma mi tra dngos //
NK036(chi)029:37: yon tan rgya mtsho nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK036(chi)029:38: chos rje ku ma r+aa dza'i zhabs la 'dud //
NK036(chi)029:39: dpal ldan tshogs gnyis yon tan rdzogs pa'i gtso //
NK036(chi)029:40: 'jig rten gsum mgon chos rje bla ma la //
NK036(chi)029:41: dad pa'i gdung shugs g.yo ba'i phyag 'tshal zhing //
NK036(chi)029:42: snying nas mchi ma 'khrugs pas skyabs su mchi //
NK036(chi)029:43: sku tshe snga ma'i snga ma dpag med nas //
NK036(chi)029:44: mtha' yas 'gro la thugs rje'i spyan dbye bas //
NK036(chi)029:45: de ring 'gro ba kun gyi gnyen gyur cig /
NK036(chi)029:46: 'dir yang sa steng 'jig rten rgyan gyur mchog /
NK036(chi)029:47: bstan pa rin chen phyogs bcur rgyas mdzad cing //
NK036(chi)029:48: rlabs chen spyod pa dam pa'i khur bsnams te //
NK036(chi)029:49: sna tshogs mdzad pas 'gro kun bde la bkod //
NK036(chi)029:50: grags dkar yon tan phreng bas gnam sa khyab //
NK036(chi)029:51: slar yang rtag par 'dzin rnams gdul bya'i phyir //
NK036(chi)029:52: tha ma'i mdzad pas shar phyogs dang lung du //
NK036(chi)029:53: chu mo lug lo'i ston zla tha chung la //
NK036(chi)029:54: mi rtag mya ngan 'da' tshul bstan par gyur //
NK036(chi)029:55: rgyan gyur 'jig rten bla ma de gshegs te //
NK036(chi)029:56: yid bzhin nor bu rin chen dbyings su stor //
NK036(chi)029:57: bstan pa rin chen dpag bsam shing chag ste //
NK036(chi)029:58: gru chen 'jig rten bla ma de ring zhig /
NK036(chi)029:59: rnam pa kun tu lha rdzas char 'bab cing //
NK036(chi)029:60: 'od zer lnga ldan ye shes snang ba gsal //
NK036(chi)029:61: lhar bcas 'jig rten ngo mtshar yid g.yos te //
NK036(chi)029:62: mkha' 'gros mchod sprin sil snyan sgra bsgrags te //
NK036(chi)029:63: sngon med snang ba ngo mtshar dpag med cing //
NK036(chi)029:64: spos bsung dri dang dus min rol mos gang //
NK036(chi)029:65: nyin mtshan khor yug 'od lnga'i mdangs shar bas //
NK036(chi)029:66: byang chub snying po 'gro ba 'dren par mdzod //
NK036(chi)029:67: sa 'di rir bcas zhi bas cher g.yos shing //
NK036(chi)029:68: nags tshal ljon shing 'dud pas phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK036(chi)029:69: me tog chu gtsang 'dzum pa'i mdangs gsal zhing //
NK036(chi)029:70: bya dang ri dwags sgra 'byin skyabs su 'gro //
NK036(chi)029:71: mkha' 'gro'i sprin phung 'du bas sngun bsus te //
NK036(chi)029:72: rig 'dzin rgyal ba'i zhing du gshegs par gyur //
NK036(chi)029:73: bstan pa'i nyi ma de ring 'dir nub ste //
NK036(chi)029:74: 'tsho byed sman gyi rgyal po gshegs kyis med //
NK036(chi)029:75: thar lam ded dpon dam pa zhig gyur cing //
NK036(chi)029:76: bde legs kun 'byung yid bzhin nor bu stor //
NK036(chi)029:77: kye ma kyi hud 'jig rten stongs kyis med //
NK036(chi)029:78: dkar phyogs ye shes nyin byed nub gyur cing //
NK036(chi)029:79: bdud rigs mun pa'i tshogs rnams rgyas gyur te //
NK036(chi)029:80: rgyal khams kun tu dus tshigs yol bar gyur //
NK036(chi)029:81: zhing de'i snang ba dam pa'ang nub gyur la //
NK036(chi)029:82: lha mi'i 'jig rten ma rig mun pas ldongs //
NK036(chi)029:83: thar gling sa mkhan chen po de med pas //
NK036(chi)029:84: da ni 'gro ba mya ngan bya ba'i rigs //
NK036(chi)029:85: rgyal ba dran dang mya ngan 'da' bsam pas //
NK036(chi)029:86: zhi ba'i gling 'gro yon tan bsam mi khyab //
NK036(chi)029:87: chos de tshad med legs par gsungs pa ste //
NK036(chi)029:88: de bas chos lhag dge tshogs rnams 'phel 'gyur //
NK036(chi)029:89: kye ma kyi hud thugs rje'i dbyings rum nas //
NK036(chi)029:90: mgon med bdag gi gdung ba'i tshig 'di gson //
NK036(chi)029:91: sna tshogs sdug bsngal mang ldan 'khor ba pa //
NK036(chi)029:92: mgon med dpung gnyen bral ba'i tshogs rnams dang //
NK036(chi)029:93: bdag cag dad ldan ltos pa'i skye dgu rnams //
NK036(chi)029:94: da ni ci bya su la re bar bya //
NK036(chi)029:95: bstan la mngon par lhags pa'i lha rnams dang //
NK036(chi)029:96: dad ldan mi rnams mya ngan mes gdungs shing //
NK036(chi)029:97: dus 'dir phan bzhed byed pa'i ljon shing chag /
NK036(chi)029:98: skyabs dang skyob pa dpung gnyen med par gyur //
NK036(chi)029:99: bdag cag gdul bya'i bsod nams mtsho bsil skam //
NK036(chi)029:100: zhi gyur rin chen bla ma dbyings su yal //
NK036(chi)029:101: chos kyi glang po de ring gzims par gyur //
NK036(chi)029:102: rang bzhin 'od gsal ye shes nyi ma nub //
NK036(chi)029:103: phan bde'i 'od dkar nub ri'i rgyab tu yol //
NK036(chi)029:104: lha mi'i bde 'byung bum pa bzang po chag /
NK036(chi)029:105: sa mkhan ded dpon rig 'dzin bla ma gshegs //
NK036(chi)029:106: gling bzhi 'jig rten rgyan gyur stongs so kye //
NK036(chi)029:107: thugs rje can yang brtse ba spongs pa bzhin //
NK036(chi)029:108: bdag cag bor nas zhing khams gzhan du gshegs //
NK036(chi)029:109: mgon med skye dgu re zhing ltos pa rnams //
NK036(chi)029:110: rang bzhin dor nas yal bar 'dor phod dam //
NK036(chi)029:111: dus min nyi zla'i 'gros kyang ma log na //
NK036(chi)029:112: sa dang bar snang dag kyang ma 'chol na //
NK036(chi)029:113: bdag can rnams la dus tshig 'di lta bu //
NK036(chi)029:114: mya ngan gdungs pas snying la khyab par gyur //
NK036(chi)029:115: gang du bsam kyang ded dpon bla ma dran //
NK036(chi)029:116: ri rtse nags kyi mthongs dang gangs ri'i 'dabs //
NK036(chi)029:117: sgrub pa'i gnas mchog sngon chad dgyes dgyes pas //
NK036(chi)029:118: sa phyogs gang na'ang deng nas yangs ma bzhugs //
NK036(chi)029:119: nye 'khor nye bar spyad pa'i tshogs mthong nas //
NK036(chi)029:120: dgyes pa'i spyan mchog gzigs par mdzad de'ang grongs //
NK036(chi)029:121: 'od gsal rin chen chos nyid bsgom bsam yang //
NK036(chi)029:122: dam pa'i gsung rnams dran nas mchi ma shor //
NK036(chi)029:123: lhar bcas 'gro ba'i bsod nams dpag bsam shing //
NK036(chi)029:124: phan bde'i yal 'dab rgyas par mi mdzad par //
NK036(chi)029:125: dus min me tog 'bras bus skom gyur te //
NK036(chi)029:126: gdul bya'i bya tshogs da ni gang du bsten //
NK036(chi)029:127: 'khor ba mi bzad sdug bsngal du ma'i phreng //
NK036(chi)029:128: bsgrod dkar zhugs la brtse bas mi gzigs par //
NK036(chi)029:129: 'jigs pa'i 'phrang las skyel mas bslus pa bzhin //
NK036(chi)029:130: bdag cag dor nas mgon po gang du gshegs //
NK036(chi)029:131: dus gsum rgyal ba kun dang dbyer med cing //
NK036(chi)029:132: dpag med mdzad pas 'gro ba'i kha lo bsgyur //
NK036(chi)029:133: mthong thos dran reg 'khor ba'i phyir bsnyil ba //
NK036(chi)029:134: yon tan rgya mtsho'i bla ma gang du gshegs //
NK036(chi)029:135: brtse ba'i thugs rje gzhan las lhag gyur cing //
NK036(chi)029:136: mdzad pa'i phrin las gnas rigs khyab par 'jug /
NK036(chi)029:137: spyan dang mngon shes spang rtogs phun sum tshogs //
NK036(chi)029:138: 'phags pa'i bla ma de ring gang du gshegs //
NK036(chi)029:139: thugs rje'i mkha' la mkhyen brtse'i sprin 'khrigs te //
NK036(chi)029:140: phyi nang gsang ba'i chos chen char 'bebs pas //
NK036(chi)029:141: ma lus 'gro ba'i re ba skong mdzad pa //
NK036(chi)029:142: mchog gyur bstan pa'i rtsa lag gang du gshegs //
NK036(chi)029:143: mgon po gangs ri'i dkyil 'khor rgyas pa la //
NK036(chi)029:144: thugs rje zhi ba bsil ba'i rgyun babs pas //
NK036(chi)029:145: 'gro kun nyon mongs me tshogs zhi mdzad pa //
NK036(chi)029:146: sa 'dzin 'jig rten gsum mgon gang du gshegs //
NK036(chi)029:147: tshogs gnyis pad rdzing yan lag brgyad ldan nas //
NK036(chi)029:148: dad ldan bung ba mang po'i tshogs rnams la //
NK036(chi)029:149: zhi bde'i dga' ston dam pa mi bgyid par //
NK036(chi)029:150: rnam grol yon tan tshogs chen gang du gshegs //
NK036(chi)029:151: sa gsum skye dgu zhi la bzhag go zhes //
NK036(chi)029:152: phan bde'i 'od stong dra ba 'gyed mdzad cing //
NK036(chi)029:153: 'gro ba'i lam yangs dkar por mdzad pa can //
NK036(chi)029:154: dge legs nyin mo'i dbang phyug gang du gshegs //
NK036(chi)029:155: 'khor tshogs dbus na cha shas gsal ba'i sku //
NK036(chi)029:156: byams pa'i zhal bzang lta bas mi ngoms la //
NK036(chi)029:157: thugs rje'i phyag gnyis 'gro la skyong mdzad pa //
NK036(chi)029:158: mgon po ston zla'i dkyil 'khor gang du gshegs //
NK036(chi)029:159: 'khor ba'i chu gter shin tu brgal dka' las //
NK036(chi)029:160: srid gsum rgya mtsho'i pha rol sgrol mdzad cing //
NK036(chi)029:161: zhi ba rin chen gling du skyel mdzad pa //
NK036(chi)029:162: gru chen mnyan pa'i rgyal po gang du gshegs //
NK036(chi)029:163: thogs med dus nas nye bar goms pa yis //
NK036(chi)029:164: 'khor ba'i gcong nad shin tu sbyang dka' bar //
NK036(chi)029:165: zhi mdzad bdud rtsi'i gsos sman kun gyi bdag /
NK036(chi)029:166: 'tsho byed sman pa'i rgyal po gang du gshegs //
NK036(chi)029:167: nyi zla'i snang bas gsal bar ma nus pa'i //
NK036(chi)029:168: gti mug mun pa rmad byung sel mdzad cing //
NK036(chi)029:169: gdul bya'i mkha' la mkhyen brtse'i rnam grol can //
NK036(chi)029:170: sngon med nam mkha'i nor bu gang du gshegs //
NK036(chi)029:171: rlabs chen mdzad pa thugs rje'i rang bzhin ni //
NK036(chi)029:172: chu srin 'dzin pa khri yis mi bskrun pa //
NK036(chi)029:173: 'byung po 'dzin ma 'di na mtshungs pa med //
NK036(chi)029:174: dpag yas skye dgu'i bla ma gang du gshegs //
NK036(chi)029:175: mi g.yo dwangs pa rgya mtsho'i rang bzhin la //
NK036(chi)029:176: 'dod 'byung nor bu'i gdengs can gtsug gis rgyan //
NK036(chi)029:177: sa steng rgyan gyur mtshungs med chos kyi rje //
NK036(chi)029:178: gzhan las che mchog bla ma gang du gshegs //
NK036(chi)029:179: bsod nams ye shes tshogs chen rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK036(chi)029:180: mthong ba tsam gyis dad pa'i rlabs g.yo zhing //
NK036(chi)029:181: 'gro kun bsod nams zhing gi mchog gyur pa //
NK036(chi)029:182: lhar bcas 'jig rten mchod sdong gang du gshegs //
NK036(chi)029:183: 'khor gyi khyams su tshangs dbyangs seng ge'i sgra //
NK036(chi)029:184: dam chos rin chen char pa 'bebs mdzad cing //
NK036(chi)029:185: ma rig the tshom d+r+wa ba gcod la mkhas //
NK036(chi)029:186: ye shes rnga sgra'i bla ma gang du gshegs //
NK036(chi)029:187: chos nyid mi g.yo ting 'dzin yangs pa'i klong //
NK036(chi)029:188: 'od gsal nyi zla dgongs klong rgya che zhing //
NK036(chi)029:189: mnyam rjes dbyer med rtag tu chos sku'i ngang //
NK036(chi)029:190: dbyings rig mthar phyin bla ma gang du gshegs //
NK036(chi)029:191: dpag med dus nas mkhyen brtse rlabs che zhing //
NK036(chi)029:192: lung rig man ngag snying po'i gangs chen mtsho //
NK036(chi)029:193: byin rlabs dngos grub rin chen 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK036(chi)029:194: yon tan rgya mtsho'i bla ma gang tu gshegs //
NK036(chi)029:195: zhi rgyas dbang drag phrin las mnga' brnyes shing //
NK036(chi)029:196: rlabs chen mdzad pas gdul bya gang du skyong //
NK036(chi)029:197: 'od gsal bstan pa phyogs bcur rgyas mdzad pa //
NK036(chi)029:198: stobs chen rgyal ba'i rnam 'phrul gang du gshegs //
NK036(chi)029:199: bdag cag dad ldan 'gro la mi gzigs par //
NK036(chi)029:200: gdod ma'i dbyings su zhi la thugs gzhol ba //
NK036(chi)029:201: brtse chen thabs mkhas thugs rje gang du gshegs //
NK036(chi)029:202: slan chad khyed zhal mthong ba'i skabs mchis sam //
NK036(chi)029:203: tha ma'i mdzad pa mngo na par skyong ba'i gnas //
NK036(chi)029:204: dge ba'i 'jig rten stong la mi gzigs sam //
NK036(chi)029:205: sdug bsngal mang ldan me tshogs spungs pa 'dir //
NK036(chi)029:206: thugs rje'i char rgyun bsil bas mi sbyong ngam //
NK036(chi)029:207: mgon gyur dag kyang re ba med mdzad na //
NK036(chi)029:208: bdag cag rnams la su zhig skyabs su gyur //
NK036(chi)029:209: kye ma skyabs mchog bla ma thugs rje can //
NK036(chi)029:210: zhi ba'i dbyings nas thugs rjes phyag rkyongs la //
NK036(chi)029:211: bdag cag 'gro kun de ring drang du gsol //
NK036(chi)029:212: 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho stongs par mdzad du gsol //
NK036(chi)029:213: de ltar gdung bas nyin mtshan gsol ba 'debs //
NK036(chi)029:214: gus pas phyag 'tshal rtag tu skyabs su mchi //
NK036(chi)029:215: bdag dang mkha' mnyam sems can thams cad kyi //
NK036(chi)029:216: dus rnams rtag tu 'dren ma chog mdzad du gsol //
NK036(chi)029:217: mtha' yas zhing dang 'gro ba ji tsam par //
NK036(chi)029:218: blo yis mngon sprul de dag thal sbyor te //
NK036(chi)029:219: dad brgya'i 'dab stong g.yo bas phyag 'tshal zhing //
NK036(chi)029:220: bstod dbyangs yan lag rgya mtshos bstod par bgyi //
NK036(chi)029:221: 'gro ba'i mgon po shin tu thugs rje can //
NK036(chi)029:222: rgyan gyur 'jig rten bla ma deng shar de //
NK036(chi)029:223: 'od gsal snying po'i bstan pa gsal mdzad nas //
NK036(chi)029:224: zhi ba'i dbyings su gshegs la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK036(chi)029:225: thugs rjes rtag tu 'khor ba yongs bzung ste //
NK036(chi)029:226: zhi ba phyogs gcig mya ngan mi 'da' bar //
NK036(chi)029:227: 'gro la phan gzigs tha ma'i mdzad pa yis //
NK036(chi)029:228: ngo mtshar 'jig rten khyab la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK036(chi)029:229: ston kha'i zla ba dang po zhi ba yis //
NK036(chi)029:230: nags khrod dam par sku tshe gtong ba las //
NK036(chi)029:231: slar yang byin rlabs thugs rjes rmad du byung //
NK036(chi)029:232: rgyal ba'i mdzad par mtshungs la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK036(chi)029:233: gang du mgon po mya ngan 'das gyur pa //
NK036(chi)029:234: de tshe sa dang nags tshal bcas pa g.yos //
NK036(chi)029:235: dus min sgra dang sil snyan dpag med 'khrol //
NK036(chi)029:236: lha rdzas mchod pas mdzes la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK036(chi)029:237: phyogs rnams ston kha'i mdog bzang mdzes pa las //
NK036(chi)029:238: dad pa'i mkha' dbyings 'od lnga'i bla re bres //
NK036(chi)029:239: d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed zlum 'khrigs za 'og ris //
NK036(chi)029:240: rab 'khyil snang ba shar la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK036(chi)029:241: sku gdung mchod las nyin mtshan phyed par yang //
NK036(chi)029:242: mkha' 'gro'i sgra dang sil snyan gling bu dang //
NK036(chi)029:243: lha rdzas rol mo 'od lnga'i snang bar bcas //
NK036(chi)029:244: ya mtshan mchod sprin mtho la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK036(chi)029:245: gang la sku gdung zhugs kyis 'bar ba na //
NK036(chi)029:246: 'od lnga'i snang bas nam mkha' khyab gyur cing //
NK036(chi)029:247: 'gro kun mi rtog bsam gtan sa la gnas //
NK036(chi)029:248: ngo mtshar snang bas khyab la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK036(chi)029:249: de tshe mkha' la snyan pa'i sgra grags cing //
NK036(chi)029:250: dus sprin rtse la 'od zer tshogs shar bas //
NK036(chi)029:251: nam mkha'i dbyings khyab khyad par nub phyogs gsal //
NK036(chi)029:252: 'gro ba'i yid rab g.yo la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK036(chi)029:253: thabs kyi sku gdung rgyas par mdzad pa las //
NK036(chi)029:254: dbu thod ril bu 'od lnga'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK036(chi)029:255: rang byon 'od lnga'i klong na rdzogs par bzhugs //
NK036(chi)029:256: ngo mtshar rten du gyur la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK036(chi)029:257: ril bu'i gdung gzhug mchod rten bzhengs pa na'ang //
NK036(chi)029:258: 'od lnga'i gdugs dang bla res rgyal mtshan mchog /
NK036(chi)029:259: nam mkha'i dbyings na snang bas mdzes gyur pa //
NK036(chi)029:260: bsod nams zhing du gyur la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK036(chi)029:261: dam pa rnams kyi tshul 'di bsam mi khyab //
NK036(chi)029:262: srid pa ji srid phan bde mdzad pa ste //
NK036(chi)029:263: 'di yi rlabs chen spyod pa mtha' yas pa //
NK036(chi)029:264: 'di lta 'o zhes bsam pa'i yul las 'das //
NK036(chi)029:265: la lar gshegs dang la lar bltams pa dang //
NK036(chi)029:266: la lar mnyam gzhag la lar zhing rnams sbyong //
NK036(chi)029:267: la lar don mdzad la lar bdud rnams 'dul //
NK036(chi)029:268: dbyings las mi g.yo sprul pa rgyun mi chad //
NK036(chi)029:269: de slad bdag cag don ldan 'gro ba rnams //
NK036(chi)029:270: 'khor ba'i gnas nas zhi ba'i nags 'dabs su //
NK036(chi)029:271: 'di yi thugs rjes myur du 'dren nges pas //
NK036(chi)029:272: dus med rgyun du gus pas gsol ba 'debs //
NK036(chi)029:273: dam pa 'di dang 'ga' zhig 'phrad gyur te //
NK036(chi)029:274: gsung tsam thos dang zhal mthong skye dgu rnams //
NK036(chi)029:275: ngan song rnams chad thar lam byang chub rnyed //
NK036(chi)029:276: de sogs yon tan brgyad kyis yongs mi langs //
NK036(chi)029:277: lhar bcas 'gro ba'i ded dpon bla ma la //
NK036(chi)029:278: bdag gzhan ma lus gus pas phyag 'tshal zhing //
NK036(chi)029:279: nam mkha'i mkha' klas ting 'dzin sprin tshogs kyis //
NK036(chi)029:280: mngon par bkang ste bla med mchod sprin bgyi //
NK036(chi)029:281: lus dang ngag yid sdig kun ci mchis pa //
NK036(chi)029:282: thugs rje'i zer gyis bsal bar mdzad du gsol //
NK036(chi)029:283: las dang nyon mongs me tshogs ji snyed kun //
NK036(chi)029:284: ye shes chu bos zhi bar mdzad du gsol //
NK036(chi)029:285: deng nas byang chub snying po mchis kyi bar //
NK036(chi)029:286: khyed kyis rnam grol thugs rjes phyag rkyongs la //
NK036(chi)029:287: 'khor ba ngan song sdug bsngal mi 'byung zhing //
NK036(chi)029:288: theg pa dman la bskyab par mdzad du gsol //
NK036(chi)029:289: rtag tu bshes gnyen dam pa brten byed cing //
NK036(chi)029:290: 'od gsal ye shes sa dang lam rdzogs nas //
NK036(chi)029:291: byang chub zhi ba thob par mdzad du gsol //
NK036(chi)029:292: bdag cag gang du skye ba rnam kun tu //
NK036(chi)029:293: khyed dang mi 'bral bsgrod pa gcig pa yis //
NK036(chi)029:294: gzhan don rlabs chen phrin las rdzogs par shog /
NK036(chi)029:295: thugs rje'i spyan mchog dam pa dkyus ring bas //
NK036(chi)029:296: dus rnams kun tu bdag cag gzigs mdzod la //
NK036(chi)029:297: nyes kun rnams sel legs dgu lhun grub nas //
NK036(chi)029:298: 'dod dgu'i re ba rdzogs par mdzad du gsol //
NK036(chi)029:299: skyabs dang skyob pa dpung gnyen mdzad du gsol //
NK036(chi)029:300: mgon dang bshes dang sa mkhan mdzad du gsol //
NK036(chi)029:301: ye shes 'od gsal sgron me sbar du gsol //
NK036(chi)029:302: 'du 'bral med par byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK036(chi)029:303: de ltar bdag blo mos pa'i gdung shugs kyis //
NK036(chi)029:304: mchog tu gus pas gsol ba btab pa yi //
NK036(chi)029:305: dge ba 'di yis bdag dang 'gro ba kun //
NK036(chi)029:306: 'chi med mya ngan med pa'i gnas thob shog /
NK036(chi)029:307: bla ma dam pa ku ma r+aa dza dgongs pa yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa'i tshe /
NK036(chi)029:308: gdung ba'i yid dang smre ngag gi sgo nas gsol
NK036(chi)029:309: ba 'debs pa'i rabs pad+ma stong ldan zhes bya ba
NK036(chi)029:310: / bla ma dam pa la mi phyed pa'i dad pa dang ldan zhing /
NK036(chi)029:311: bde bar gshegs pa'i gsung rab phal mo che thos pa dang /
NK036(chi)029:313: sgom pa las byung ba'i shes rab legs par sbyangs pa /
NK036(chi)029:314: kun mkhyen ngag gi dbang pos sbyar ba 'di yongs su rdzogs so //
